# SmokeSense MQTT Access Control List
# Controls which users can publish/subscribe to which topics

# Bridge service — can read everything, publish commands
user bridge
topic read smokesense/#
topic write smokesense/#

# DataGuard devices — can only publish their own telemetry
user dataguard
topic write smokesense/+/+/telemetry
topic write smokesense/+/+/event
topic write smokesense/+/+/status
topic write smokesense/+/+/heartbeat
topic read smokesense/+/+/cmd
topic read smokesense/+/+/config

# Node devices — same permissions as DataGuard
user node
topic write smokesense/+/+/telemetry
topic write smokesense/+/+/event
topic write smokesense/+/+/status
topic write smokesense/+/+/heartbeat
topic read smokesense/+/+/cmd
topic read smokesense/+/+/config

# Gateway devices
user gateway
topic write smokesense/+/+/telemetry
topic write smokesense/+/+/event
topic write smokesense/+/+/status
topic write smokesense/+/+/heartbeat
topic read smokesense/+/+/cmd
topic read smokesense/+/+/config

# Admin — full access (for debugging)
user admin
topic readwrite #
